      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior presents well, though it does show minor signs of regular use, such as a few small stone chips on the hood and some light surface scratches near the door handles. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of odors, with only slight wear visible on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. Mechanically, the car is sound, providing a smooth and reliable driving experience. It\u2019s an excellent option for someone looking for a dependable, well-cared-for vehicle that is ready for the road.",
