      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I'm selling my absolute gem of a car, and let me tell you, it is in pristine condition! It looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014I've babied this beauty from day one. It drives incredibly smooth and is spotless inside and out. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come see it in person!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
