    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, boasting a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like finish and absolutely zero paint chips or imperfections. The interior is equally pristine, featuring supple, uncreased leather and high-definition displays that still retain their factory clarity. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; every service has been performed ahead of schedule at certified dealerships, with a comprehensive binder of documentation included. From the spotless engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this car offers a driving experience identical to the day it rolled off the assembly line. A rare find for the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
